item.title: How do I change the ip of a server so it will run for me?
item.dc:creator: @Xdivinex Xdivinex
item.description:
@Xdivinex wrote:

ok if you want to change ip on the client you need to go to class68_20_15.java and loader.java

search string ip it should show like “127.0.0.1” or “0.0.0.0”

Change it to the ip that you have created on no-ip.com

If you change it correctly and it still doesnt work dont worry it’s not just you a lot of people have this problem. everyone else will be able to login in still just change the ip for yourself back to “127.0.0.1”
